title: The Inspector vol. 1 - Pink Panther Classic Cartoon Collection
description:
MGM earned my displeasure by not keeping in print "The Pink Panther Classic Cartoon Collection," and I will have my vengeance uploads! These are some of the best cartoons ever and it's a crime to make them difficult or too expensive to get. So let's put them back in print, shall we?

This is a .rar of an uncompressed full rip of the Region 1 DVD. It contains the first 17, AND BEST, Inspector animated shorts. Seriously, I'll put up "Part Deux" later, but it's for completists only - Volume 1 is the good stuff.

Seed and your seeds will seed, and the seeds will spread, and the torrent will be strong.
